node.text:
If you truly want to be great, spend every waking hour helping others to be great first.🔥🤔💯😏

So many people want to be Kings and Queens yet they do not know how to be Servants. And they will fail because they desire power but not responsibility. Even worse, they want power for themselves and not for the good of others. This attitude is not only arrogant but will surely lead to destruction.

node.text:
I am so grateful to God for all the Blessings he has bestowed upon me and just simply Blessed to be a humble servant🙏🏾 

My prayer is that I am fully fulfilling the purpose He has over my life. Super Greatful for all that he is doing and will continue to do 💎

I hope I am inspiring someone out there to know that through Faith AND Work All things are possible. This morning I did something I rarely ever do. I looked back on my life and smelled the roses 🌹 and thought to myself like wow! To be able to help impacted and changed thousands of lives, and I am beyond blessed to have such an amazing support system and the best is Still yet to come‼️
